wikipedia_page.main:
Darren Davis (born 5 February 1967) is an English former professional footballer who played for Maidstone United, Notts County, Lincoln City and Scarborough.In June 2002 he was appointed manager of Gedling Town.
He is currently Assistant Manager of the Notts County's Centre of Excellence.
